Project Title: -
        Quiz Game.

•	Project Definition
•	Project Overview 
Objective:
The objective of this project is to design and develop an interactive Quiz Game application that allows users to answer questions, test their knowledge, and 
receive instant feedback. The project aims to make learning more engaging and enjoyable through a simple and user-friendly interface. It also helps in understanding 
basic software development concepts by creating a complete working application.
Scope:
The scope of this project includes creating a quiz game with multiple questions, answer options, scoring, and result display. The application can be expanded
later with features such as timers, categories, difficulty levels, and leaderboards. It can run on web browsers and be made responsive for different devices.
The project can also be improved by adding more topics and interactive elements.

•	Problem Statement
Many students find it difficult to stay engaged with traditional study methods because they often do not provide instant feedback or interactive learning.
Text-based learning alone may feel boring and less effective for revision. Therefore, a Quiz Game is needed to make learning fun, active, and self-assessment
based. The application should allow users to attempt questions and check their performance immediately.

