•	Applications
  •	Interactive learning for students through quick question-and-answer practice.
  •	Self-assessment tool for users to test their knowledge on different topics.
  •	Classroom support for teachers to make revision more engaging.
  •	Exam preparation aid for competitive tests and subject-wise revision.
  •	A simple game-based platform that improves focus and participation.

•	Future Enhancements
   •	Add a time for each question to make the game more challenging.
   •	Include multiple categories like science, math, GK, and technology.
   •	Add difficulty levels such as easy, medium, and hard.
   •	Store user scores and create a leaderboard.
   •	Improve the interface with animations, sounds, and better visuals.
   •	Add login functionality and save user progress. 

•	Conclusion
The Quiz Game project is a simple and effective application that combines learning with entertainment. It helps users test their knowledge, receive instant
feedback, and stay engaged in a fun way. The project also provides practical experience in web development and can be improved further with advanced features.






